quran[3{c,v,t}:
24,59,aur jab tumahray larke baaligh ho jaien to un ko bhi isi terhan ijazat leni chahiye jis terhan un se aglay ( yani barray aadmi ) ijazat haasil karte rahay hain. is terhan khuda tum se apni ayatain khol khol kar sunataa hai. aur khuda jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai
24,60,"aur barri Umar ki aurtain jin ko nikah ki tawaqqa nahi rahi, aur woh kapray utaar kar sir nanga karliya karen to un par kuch gunah nahi bashart e kay apni zeenat ki cheezein nah zahir karen. aur is se bhi bachchen to yeh un ke haq mein behtar hai. aur khuda santa aur jaanta hai"
24,61,nah to andhay par kuch gunah hai aur nah lngrhe par aur nah bemaar par aur nah khud tum par ke apne gharon se khana khao ya apne bapon ke gharon se ya apni maaon ke gharon se ya bhaiyon ke gharon se ya apni behnoon ke gharon se ya apne chchaon ke gharon se ya apni پھوپھیوں ke gharon se ya apne mamoon ke gharon se ya apni khalaaon ke gharon se ya is ghar se jis ki knjyan tumahray haath mein hon ya apne doston ke gharon se ( aur is ka bhi ) tum par kuch gunah nahi ke sab mil kar khana khao ya judda judda. aur jab gharon mein jaya karo to apne ( ghar walon ko ) salamkiya karo. ( yeh ) khuda ki taraf se mubarak aur pakeeza tohfa hai. is terhan khuda apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum samjhoo
